Design patch modules
Read a midi file
Playback/Render sound

Sound-designer intends to facilitate a music writing/production workflow.  
It has the ability to generate scores that are a pdf file, process that score as a  midi files
against sounds designed using digital signal processing.

How to configure and install i

An example of how to use it or get it running
To write a score. Open a .ly file in the src directory.
To generate the score and pdf file run the command comply
which lives in bin/ from the root dir.

